      "text": "Yeah there's a _very_ simple trick for this, but it's not at all obvious.\n\nPart 1.  Only use monospaced fonts.\nPart 2.  Use the golden ratio to compute character size\n\nThen it's:\n\n$w = [Math]::Ceiling(($LineLength * $size)/$goldenRatio)\n$h = [Math]::Ceiling(($totalLines + 2) * $size * $Spacing)"
